WEBVTT

1
00:02:34.320 --> 00:02:35.738
Let me get that for you.

2
00:02:41.035 --> 00:02:43.370
What did you pack?
We're only here two days.

3
00:02:43.371 --> 00:02:45.915
I like to be prepared.

4
00:02:55.341 --> 00:02:57.885
I'll clean it.
I'm sure it's expensive--

5
00:02:57.886 --> 00:03:00.512
Don't worry. it's a fake.

6
00:03:00.513 --> 00:03:01.889
But I thought you were rich.

7
00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:04.224
No. I'm not.

8
00:03:04.225 --> 00:03:08.897
- I live in the same neighborhood as you.
- Really?

9
00:08:32.470 --> 00:08:34.847
You thought
I was rich and dumb?

10
00:08:35.932 --> 00:08:37.892
I'll give you a pass 'cause you're cute.

11
00:16:07.091 --> 00:16:08.466
I found the letter!

12
00:16:08.467 --> 00:16:09.551
What letter?

13
00:16:10.177 --> 00:16:11.386
It's okay.

14
00:16:11.387 --> 00:16:13.514
I feel the same way.

15
00:16:16.058 --> 00:16:19.603
Dae. you can be honest with me!
Like what's written in the letter...

16
00:16:27.444 --> 00:16:29.237
Oh. Dae!

17
00:16:29.238 --> 00:16:32.116
Can... I see that letter?

18
00:16:34.535 --> 00:16:35.868
It doesn't have a name on it.

19
00:16:35.869 --> 00:16:39.415
Dae. I know it's for me. Look.

20
00:17:21.165 --> 00:17:22.081
So...

21
00:17:22.082 --> 00:17:25.334
Of course.
it's a little soon for love letters.

22
00:17:25.335 --> 00:17:29.256
When we get back to Seoul.
would you like to get dinner with me?

23
00:17:33.052 --> 00:17:36.638
Wait a minute.
if you didn't write this. whose is this?

24
00:17:38.474 --> 00:17:40.059
What are you guys talking about?
